channel.title: Help With Project Frozn Fury Client
channel.description:
Hey everyone I saw this tutorial http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/tutorials/253018-how-make-your-project-insanity-client-webclient.html and it said I could setup my client so I could jar it and make it a webclient. So I did everything right and I jarred it. But when I run the jar file nothing shows up. So if anyone can help me or referr me to a tutorial to help that would be great because nothing in the client was ready to be jarred for a webclient.
Thanks for reading.
